file.name: idkit_v1-openapi_spec.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
    title: IDKIT API Swagger Specification
    description: DEFAULT
    version: 1.0.0
servers:
    - url: https://example.api.au.idkit.com/api/v1
tags:
    - name: transactions
      description: Operations about Transactions
paths:
    /transactions:
        post:
            security:
              - oAuth2ClientCredentials:
                - 'transactions/post'
            tags:
                - transactions
            summary: Create a transaction
            description: Triggers an ID verification, either as an SMS we will send to your customers or as a link which you can pass on or redirect your customer to however you like.
            operationId: create
            requestBody:
                description: Create Transaction Parameters
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            required:
                                - flow_type
                            type: object
                            properties:
                                flow_type:
                                    type: string
                                name:
                                    type: string
                                    description: You can specify a "name" reference that may be seen in the SMS and is stored in the transaction record. (eg. Daniel).
                                notifications:
                                    required:
                                        - complete
                                    type: object
                                    properties:
                                        complete:
                                            type: array
                                            items:
                                                required:
                                                    - auth_header_name
                                                type: object
                                                properties:
                                                    auth_header_name:
                                                        type: string
                                                        description: Optional Name of an authorization header for us to use when contacting your webhook URL.
                                                    auth_header_value:
                                                        type: string
                                                        description: Optional Value of an authorization header for us to use when contacting your webhook URL.
                                                    type:
                                                        type: string
                                                    url:
                                                        type: string
                                                        description: Your webhook URL for where we should send the notification that the transaction has been completed.
                                phone_number:
                                    type: string
                                    desctiption: The mobile number without region code (eg. 0400123456 or 400123456).
                                phone_region_code:
                                    type: string
                                    description: The region code for the mobile number (eg. +61)
                                redirect_url_exit:
                                    type: string
                                    description: A URL for the customer to be redirected to if exiting within the journey without completing.
                                redirect_url_success:
                                    type: string
                                    description: A URL for the customer to be redirected to once successfully completing the journey.
                                reference:
                                    type: string
                                    desctiption: You can specify a reference that may be seen in the SMS and is stored in the transaction record. (eg. 0000001).
                        examples:
                            sample:
                                $ref: '#/components/examples/CreateTransactionRequestBody'
                required: true
            responses:
                200:
                    description: OK
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateTransactionResponse'
                            example:
                                transaction_id: 01ERZZN650QZM9N7C20E4G8760
                                url: https://example.idkit.com/01ERZZN650QZM9N7C20E4G8760
                400:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
                401:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthenticated'
                500:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/InternalServerError'
    /transactions/{transaction_id}/{format}:
        get:
            security:
              - oAuth2ClientCredentials:
                - 'transactions/get'
            tags:
                - transactions
            summary: Fetch a transaction
            description: Get the transaction payload data by `trasanction_id`. You can generate a PDF (Base64 data) by setting the `format` to "pdf".
            operationId: get
            parameters:
                - name: transaction_id
                  in: path
                  description: Transaction ID
                  required: true
                  schema:
                      type: string
                  example: 01ERZZN650QZM9N7C20E4G8760
                - name: format
                  in: path
                  description: 'Available values are: json, pdf'
                  schema:
                      default: json
                      type: string
                  example: json
            responses:
                200:
                    description: OK
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                oneOf:
                                    - $ref: '#/components/schemas/GetTransactionJson'
                                    - $ref: '#/components/schemas/GetTransactionPDF'
                            examples:
                                'JSON Example':
                                    $ref: '#/components/examples/GetTransactionJSONExample'
                                'PDF Example':
                                    $ref: '#/components/examples/GetTransactionPDFExample'
                400:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
                401:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthenticated'
                404:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthenticated'
                500:
                    $ref: '#/components/responses/InternalServerError'
components:
    schemas:
        DataProviderData:
            required:
                - DATA_CONNECT
            type: object
            properties:
                DATA_CONNECT:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataProvider'
                GREEN_ID:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataProvider'
                ID_MATRIX:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataProvider'
            description: Model for DataProvider
        SearchResults:
            required:
                - fraudassessment
            type: object
            properties:
                fraudassessment:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Components'
                verification:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Verification'
            description: Model for SearchResults
        IdMatrixResults:
            required:
                - overall
            type: object
            properties:
                overall:
                    type: string
                rulesResults:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/RulesResults'
                searchResults:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/SearchResults'
                verificationOutcome:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/VerificationOutcome'
            description: Model for SearchResults
        IdMatrixData:
            required:
                - fraudAssessment
            type: object
            properties:
                fraudAssessment:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/FraudAssessment'
                overall:
                    type: string
                searchResults:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/IdMatrixResults'
                summary:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Summary'
            description: Model for IdMatrix
        Summary:
            required:
                - name
            type: object
            properties:
                name:
                    type: string
                value:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Summary
        VerificationOutcome:
            required:
                - indicator
            type: object
            properties:
                indicator:
                    type: string
                totalPoints:
                    type: string
            description: Model for VerificationOutcome
        Verification:
            required:
                - components
            type: object
            properties:
                components:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Components'
                name:
                    type: string
                points:
                    type: string
                results:
                    type: string
                searchName:
                    type: string
                value:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Verification
        RulesResults:
            required:
                - name
            type: object
            properties:
                name:
                    type: string
                value:
                    type: string
            description: Model for RulesResults
        Overall:
            required:
                - name
            type: object
            properties:
                name:
                    type: string
                value:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Overall
        FraudAssessment:
            required:
                - dataSource
            type: object
            properties:
                dataSource:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataSource'
                overall:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Overall'
            description: Model for FraudAssessment
        DataSource:
            required:
                - name
            type: object
            properties:
                name:
                    type: string
                result:
                    type: string
                score:
                    type: string
                threshold:
                    type: string
                weight:
                    type: string
            description: Model for DataSource
        GreenIdData:
            required:
                - individualResults
            type: object
            properties:
                individualResults:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/IndividualResults'
                overall:
                    type: string
                registrationDetails:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/RegistrationDetails'
            description: Model for GreenIdData
        RegistrationDetails:
            required:
                - label
            type: object
            properties:
                label:
                    type: string
                value:
                    type: string
            description: Model for RegistrationDetails
        IndividualResults:
            required:
                - background
            type: object
            properties:
                background:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: string
                dvs:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Dvs'
                watchlist:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Watchlist'
            description: Model for IndividualResults
        Watchlist:
            required:
                - ERROR
            type: object
            properties:
                ERROR:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: string
                FOUND_ON_LIST:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: string
                NOT_FOUND_ON_LIST:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: string
            description: Model for Watchlist
        Components:
            required:
                - address
            type: object
            properties:
                address:
                    type: string
                dob:
                    type: string
                firstName:
                    type: string
                fraud:
                    type: string
                full_name:
                    type: string
                id:
                    type: string
                name:
                    type: string
                surName:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Components
        Dvs:
            required:
                - components
            type: object
            properties:
                components:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Components'
                label:
                    type: string
                result:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Dvs
        Documents:
            required:
                - asf_breakdown
            type: object
            properties:
                asf_breakdown:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/AsfBreakdown'
                created_at:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
                document_id:
                    type: string
                extracted:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Extracted'
                face_photo:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/File'
                front_document:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/File'
                identity_document_type:
                    type: string
                ocr:
                    type: boolean
                original_front_document:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/File'
                updated_at:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
            description: Model for Documents
        File:
            required:
                - content_type
            type: object
            properties:
                content_type:
                    type: string
                size:
                    type: integer
                    format: int32
                url:
                    type: string
            description: Model for File
        DataProvider:
            required:
                - data
            type: object
            properties:
                data:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataConnectData'
                message:
                    type: string
                overall:
                    type: string
                version:
                    type: string
                xml:
                    type: boolean
            description: Model for DataConnect
        DataConnectData:
            required:
                - fieldDetails
            type: object
            properties:
                fieldDetails:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/FieldDetails'
                rapidID:
                    type: string
                VerifyDocumentResult:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/VerifyDocumentResult'
            description: Model for DataConnectData
        FieldDetails:
            required:
                - BirthDate
            type: object
            properties:
                BirthDate:
                    type: string
                BirthDay:
                    type: string
                BirthMonth:
                    type: string
                BirthYear:
                    type: string
                CardType:
                    type: string
                CountryOfIssue:
                    type: string
                ExpiryDay:
                    type: string
                FamilyName:
                    type: string
                GivenName:
                    type: string
                ImmiCardNumber:
                    type: string
                LicenceNumber:
                    type: string
                MiddleName:
                    type: string
                RegistrationState:
                    type: string
                StateOfIssue:
                    type: string
            description: Model for FieldDetails
        Attributes:
            required:
                - i_type
            type: object
            properties:
                i_type:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Attributes
        VerifyDocumentResult:
            required:
                - ActivityId
            type: object
            properties:
                ActivityId:
                    type: string
                attributes:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Attributes'
                OriginatingAgencyCode:
                    type: string
                VerificationRequestNumber:
                    type: string
                VerificationResultCode:
                    type: string
            description: Model for VerifyDocumentResult
        Results:
            required:
                - data
            type: object
            properties:
                data:
                    type: string
                documents:
                    type: string
                facematch:
                    type: string
                liveness:
                    type: string
                overall:
                    type: string

        LikenessFeatures:

                jaw:
                    type: string
                left_brow:
                    type: string
                left_cheek:
                    type: string
                left_eye:
                    type: string
                middle_forehead:
                    type: string
                mouth:
                    type: string
                nose:
                    type: string
                philtrum:
                    type: string
                right_brow:
                    type: string
                right_cheek:
                    type: string
                right_eye:
                    type: string
            description: Model for LikenessFeatures
        AsfBreakdown:
            required:
                - detail_check
            type: object
            properties:
                detail_check:
                    type: string
                document_integrity:
                    type: string
                image_composition:
                    type: string
                photo_check:
                    type: string
            description: Model for AsfBreakdown
        Extracted:
            required:
                - address
            type: object
            properties:
                address:
                    type: string
                card_number:
                    type: string
                city:
                    type: string
                country_of_issue:
                    type: string
                date_of_birth:
                    type: string
                date_of_expiry:
                    type: string
                document_type:
                    type: string
                first_name:
                    type: string
                issuer:
                    type: string
                last_name:
                    type: string
                licence_class:
                    type: string
                licence_condition:
                    type: string
                licence_number:
                    type: string
                middle_name:
                    type: string
                state:
                    type: string
                street:
                    type: string
                zip_code:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Extracted
        GetTransactionJson:
            required:
                - created_at
            type: object
            properties:
                created_at:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
                current_step:
                    type: string
                data_provider:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DataProviderData'
                device_info:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeviceInfo'
                documents:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Documents'
                facematch_best_frame:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/File'
                flow_type:
                    type: string
                likeness_features:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/LikenessFeatures'
                likeness_overall:
                    type: string
                liveness_attempts:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/LivenessAttempts'
                results:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Results'
                spoof_result:
                    type: string
                status:
                    type: string
                transaction_id:
                    type: string
                user_details:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserDetails'
            description: Model for Get Transaction as JSON
        GetTransactionPDF:
            required:
                - created_at
            type: object
            properties:
                created_at:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
                flow_type:
                    type: string
                status:
                    type: string
                transaction_id:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Get Transaction as JSON
        LivenessAttempts:
            required:
                - actions
            type: object
            properties:
                actions:
                    type: array
                    items:
                        type: string
                result:
                    type: boolean
                session_id:
                    type: string
                video:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/File'
            description: Model for LivenessAttempts
        UserDetails:
            required:
                - address
            type: object
            properties:
                address:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Address'
                date_of_birth:
                    type: string
                    format: date
                date_of_expiry:
                    type: string
                    format: date
                first_name:
                    type: string
                last_name:
                    type: string
                licence_number:
                    type: string
                middle_name:
                    type: string
                passport_number:
                    type: string
            description: Model for UserDetails
        Address:
            required:
                - city
            type: object
            properties:
                city:
                    type: string
                country:
                    type: string
                full_address:
                    type: string
                post_code:
                    type: string
                state:
                    type: string
                street_address:
                    type: string
                street_address_2:
                    type: string
                suburb:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Address
        DeviceInfo:
            required:
                - browser
            type: object
            properties:
                browser:
                    type: string
                country:
                    type: string
                geolocation:
                    type: string
                ip:
                    type: string
                ip_location:
                    type: string
                isp:
                    type: string
                os:
                    type: string
                vpn:
                    type: boolean
            description: Model for DeviceInfo
        CreateTransactionResponse:
            required:
                - transaction_id
            type: object
            properties:
                transaction_id:
                    type: string
                url:
                    type: string
            description: Model for Create
        BadRequestResponse:
            type: object
            properties:
                message:
                    type: string
                    example: Bad Request.
        UnauthenticatedResponse:
            type: object
            properties:
                message:
                    type: string
                    example: Unauthenticated.
        NotFoundResponse:
            type: object
            properties:
                message:
                    type: string
                    example: The token was not found.
        InternalServerErrorResponse:
            type: object
            properties:
                message:
                    type: string
                    example: Internal Server Error.
    responses:
        BadRequest:
            description: The server could not understand the request due to invalid syntax.
            content:
                application/json:
                    schema:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/BadRequestResponse'
        Unauthenticated:
            description: Although the HTTP standard specifies "unauthorized", semantically this response means "unauthenticated". That is, the client must authenticate itself to get the requested response.
            content:
                application/json:
                    schema:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/UnauthenticatedResponse'
        NotFound:
            description: The server can not find requested resource.
            content:
                application/json:
                    schema:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/NotFoundResponse'
        InternalServerError:
            description: The server has encountered a situation it doesn't know how to handle.
            content:
                application/json:
                    schema:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/InternalServerErrorResponse'
